column2: DemocracyOS is an online space for deliberation and voting on political proposals. The software aims to stimulate better arguments and come to better rulings.

Updating ./lib/fixtures/topics.json

Previously, `./lib/fixtures/topics.json` was in the old V1 format. It could not be loaded according to the steps in [the instructions](https://github.com/DemocracyOS/democracyos/wiki/Load-fixtures).

This converts `topics.json` to the most recent format, following the steps in [`migrateV1`](https://github.com/DemocracyOS/democracyos/blob/master/lib/migrations/topic.js#L59).

Fixes #1176.

Adding forum-reserved-names.js
Previously: `models (fn)` tries to load `./lib/models/forum-reserved-names.js` and treat it as a function. This doesn't work.
This adds `forum-reserved-names-.js` to the list of exceptions to skip (`except`, line 137 of `dos-db`).
Fixes #1171.
